title: Fifty Years in the Doghouse by Lloyd Alexander (.epub)
description:
Fifty Years in the Doghouse by Lloyd Alexander

Requirements: .ePUB Reader

Overview: Fifty years ago, William Michael Ryan joined the staff of the American Society for the Prevention of Cruelty to Animals, or, as it is affectionately known to its friends, the "Doghouse." Today he is Special Agent No. 1. This frequently touching, often hilarious, and always entertaining book describes Ryan's adventures with animals during this span of half a century -- adventures that have brought him into contact with more than half a million beasts, birds, and reptiles.

Genre: Non-Fiction > Biography
